description.text: The majestic towers, winding paths and narrow bridges of Elf City await you. Two Cubes and a Base!

ru.original: The majestic towers, winding paths and narrow bridges of Elf City await you. Two Cubes and a Base!
ru.translation: Причудливые башни, извилистые тропы и узкие мостики — это город эльфов. Два куба и база.

es.original: The majestic towers, winding paths and narrow bridges of Elf City await you. Two Cubes and a Base!
es.translation:
Admira la majestuosidad de la ciudad elfa.
Dos generadores y un núcleo.

de.original: The majestic towers, winding paths and narrow bridges of Elf City await you. Two Cubes and a Base!
de.translation: Die majestätischen Türme, Brücken und gewundenen Wege der Elfenstadt! Zwei Generatoren und eine Basis.

pt.original: The majestic towers, winding paths and narrow bridges of Elf City await you. Two Cubes and a Base!
pt.translation: As torres majestosas, os caminhos sinuosos e as pontes estreitas da Cidade dos Elfos lhe aguardam. Dois Cubos e uma Base!

fr.original: The majestic towers, winding paths and narrow bridges of Elf City await you. Two Cubes and a Base!
fr.translation: Les tours majestueuses, les chemins tortueux et les ponts étroits de la cité elfe vous attendent. Deux cubes et une base.
